Pulse sensor node class for tessel:
    The PulseSensor collects some pulse samples. When it has enough samples to determine BPM (beats per minute), it declares ready. It then logs an updated BPM estimate at each
    heartbeat and toggles the blue LED in time.
  https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Frijol/PulseSensor/master/index.js
  
Wifi connection:
         https://github.com/echalkpad/website-down-alarm

Sensor object model ( best ble modeule)
         https://github.com/echalkpad/sensorjs-ble
         https://github.com/echalkpad/sensorjs

